Ivor Lewis operation for epidermoid carcinoma of the esophagus.

Lozac'h P(1), Topart P, Etienne J, Charles JF.

Author information:
(1)Department of Surgery, Centre Hospitalo-Universitaire, Brest, France.

One hundred patients, 95 men and 5 women with a mean age of 59 years (age range, 
35 to 77 years), were treated by the same initiate surgeon in practice from 1982 
